#: ajax/periodicityfields.php:170
msgid ""
"For months having less days than the selected day, the export will be done "
"on the last day of the month."
msgstr ""
"Pour les mois plus court que le jour sélectionné, l'export sera fait le "
"dernier jour du mois."

#: ajax/periodicityfields.php:177
